<title>USA: Calvin Klein names Lawrence DeParis CFO.</title>
<headline>Calvin Klein names Lawrence DeParis CFO.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Calvin Klein Inc said Monday that it had appointed Lawrence DeParis as chief financial officer and senior vice president of finance, effective April 14.</p>
<p>Before joining Calvin Klein, DeParis was the chief financial officer and chief administrative officer for Escada (USA) Inc.</p>
<p>He succeeds Robin Orlick, who was recently named Senior Vice President, Licensing, Calvin Klein said.</p>
